{"tid":667522,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone終結者！Nokia X6","createTime":"2018-05-16T23:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T23:09:57.000Z","uid":59919,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4af39b2a961c0d67cd628348e436d95e94bd5706","tid":667522,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/072902_f145d93a0a9ef7a666b6e730d8a91f7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F072902_f145d93a0a9ef7a666b6e730d8a91f7e.jpg&h=f68bc612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNokia X6 正式發佈，Nokia X6 是廠商首款使用全屏設計的新手機，Nokia X6 採用 5.8 吋 19:9 屏幕，解像度為 2,280 x 1,080，機身前後均使用第三代 Gorilla Glass 強化玻璃，官方指 Nokia X6 玻璃覆蓋率達到 95%，而中框則使用鋁合金，並提供暗夜藍、極地白及星空黑三種配色，機身大小為 147.23 x 70.96 x 7.99mm，基本上仍可單手操作。<br />\n<br />\n配 Snapdragon 636 處理器<br />\n<br />\nNokia X6 使用 Snapdragon 636 處理器，時脈為 1.8GHz，內建 Adreno509 GPU，最高配備 6GB 記憶體及 64GB eMMC 5.1 快閃儲存，內建 3,060mAh 電池，並支援 QC 3.0 快充技術，配 Android 8.0 Oreo。定價方面，Nokia X6 4GB+32GB 版定價 1,299 人民幣 (約 HK$1,601)、4GB+64GB 版 1,499 人民幣 (約 HK$1,848)、6GB+64GB 版 1,699 人民幣 (約 HK$2,094)，定價與紅米 Note 5 相近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/072918_158a0ca6bdf4846ce9b4fd03441fc893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F072918_158a0ca6bdf4846ce9b4fd03441fc893.jpg&h=d4acb154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/072925_e7ef85fab8e7afc812ddfbeadf12449b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F072925_e7ef85fab8e7afc812ddfbeadf12449b.jpg&h=f0af07bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙攝像頭<br />\n<br />\n拍攝功能方面，Nokia X6 後置 1,600 萬加 500 萬像素雙像頭，支持 EIS 影片防震，採用黑白加彩色方案，支援先拍後對焦。前置鏡頭，則為 1,600 萬像素，具有 6 種影棚燈光效果，並支持 AI 美顏，可應用智能 3D 虛疑化運算法，提供智能人像打光、圖片模糊，景深虛化等功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/072943_382fcdf895ac3aa83d14707135425726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F072943_382fcdf895ac3aa83d14707135425726.jpg&h=fee0f2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於有新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431a1ce7d402d04c0f0673537037f93b9de4304e","tid":667522,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:36:21.000Z","msg":"再勁咪又係唔係行iOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a3f44f31c2c292b066b03a9cb87cde9b0d2ad3","tid":667522,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c956b36be9af863a8108788070924355df69ba4","tid":667522,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:44:38.000Z","msg":"連大佬845都未夠a11鬥<br />\n636<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb606b9d2ad4ee9cbe41555367af23d08b25569d","tid":667522,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:53:14.000Z","msg":"幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d4c82223ad0485415c6677de3c308ff2009506","tid":667522,"uid":143572,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"又係M字額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5335268a79434b458eaec8e96bf3a9ebc7a889","tid":667522,"uid":105219,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:56:28.000Z","msg":"2018年都重用緊第三代 Gorilla Glass<br />\n<br />\n而且又係M字。。。唉。。 點解班designer要跟apple一樣咁7"},{"pid":"91c6fb0cb523c1d87ae51dbc262ae9df65c3975e","tid":667522,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:57:41.000Z","msg":"中階機黎 成班見標題就認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520e84e565ba015087b63cfabedb94aac49eb697","tid":667522,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91c6fb0cb523c1d87ae51dbc262ae9df65c3975e","tid":667522,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:57:41.000Z","msg":"中階機黎 成班見標題就認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:07:39.000Z","msg":"果班idog嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8ee6aa6a0707fc4c0de216f0dc6727317de691","tid":667522,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:24:25.000Z","msg":"有行貨可能會屌部 但有冇nfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139b1116a5fad562469fda14f4507d90f1357bdf","tid":667522,"uid":92005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"同zenfone 5比 邊部勁啲"},{"pid":"e7f79065c80c8bb0aca290e56698fece9830b8ae","tid":667522,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"又係m字額，唔會考慮，等pixel 3"},{"pid":"d5d0d799c7bca4e68911c993738abfea36b1184d","tid":667522,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"全屏（有下巴）<br />\n<br />\nOn9 設計"},{"pid":"733d8d882f3228dc5c0912b8bc7897533c479653","tid":667522,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"有m又下巴<br />\n鏡頭無特別<br />\n疑似無nfc<br />\n唔考慮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176dd989fb1018d32da5c7d76512b8b1f68d54d0","tid":667522,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91c6fb0cb523c1d87ae51dbc262ae9df65c3975e","tid":667522,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:57:41.000Z","msg":"中階機黎 成班見標題就認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"咁耐都無人post 09年篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如今能跟 iPhone 相提並論的大螢幕觸控音樂手機不多，iPhone 已經第三年登上機皇的寶座，難道就沒有一款手機從 iPhone 手裡將機皇的寶座搶回來嗎？ Nokia 大會上最先發佈的這款 Nokia X6 就具備這樣的實力。<br />\nNokia X6 有紅黑、藍白兩種顏色可供選擇，該機採用 Symbian OS v9.4 操作系統，基於 S60 5th Edition 平台。X6 的機身厚度只有 13.8mm，相比前作 N97、5800 XpressMusic 都要薄很多，相比 iPhone 還是略厚。另外，X6 能連續播放音樂達 35 小時，與 iPhone 相當。"},{"pid":"31e02641b9686fc303bc3dc0294ff2e6fd5ce7b2","tid":667522,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T23:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}